x = rnorm(500)
y = rnorm(500)
vec_logic_1 = ifelse((x + y) > 1, TRUE, FALSE)
num = as.numeric(vec_logic_1)
fac = as.factor(vec_logic_1)
question_2_df = tibble(
  x,
  y,
  vec_logic_1,
  num,
  fac
)

This dataset contain 500 rows and 5 columns. The mean of x is 0.0021022. The median of x is 0.0469736. The standard deviation of x is 1.0207772. The proportion of cases for which x + y > 1 is 0.248.

ggplot(question_2_df, aes(x = x, y = y, color = "red")) + geom_point()

ggsave("myplot.pdf")
